      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――星見市",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Hoshimi City",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.03333333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "あーっ！　やっぱり海はいいね～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ahh! The sea is the best!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_03-mei001.m4a",
      "text": "いかにも、夏って感じで！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It just screams summer!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_03-mei002.m4a",
      "text": "うんうん、ここに来て正解だよ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yup‚ we were right to come here.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "確かに夏は凄く感じられるんだけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It certainly feels very summery here‚ but…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.866666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_03-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "暑過ぎて、曲作りに集中出来ないんじゃ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "it’s too hot to focus on making the song…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.733333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "そうですね……新曲作りのヒントは海にある！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’re right‚ “the hint for making the new song is in the sea!”",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_03-ski001.m4a",
      "text": "って芽衣ちゃんが言うから、来てみましたけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "as Mei-chan said…so here we are…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.133333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "早く新曲のイメージを掴んで、曲作りを",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We have to capture an image for the new song quickly‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.966666666666665,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_03-ngs001.m4a",
      "text": "手配してもらわないといけないね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "and make arrangements for writing the new song.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 34.233333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "あっ、あそこでかき氷売ってる！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey‚ they’re selling shaved ice over there!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.63333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_03-mei003.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣食べたい！　みんなの分も買ってくるね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I want to eat some! I’ll go and buy some for all of us.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.46666666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3899.9999999999986
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "あっ、芽衣、私達、遊びに来た訳じゃ――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But Mei‚ we didn’t actually come here to play…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_03-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "って、もういない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ she’s gone.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.03333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "まぁまぁ、琴乃ちゃん。今まで、ずっと",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well Kotono-chan‚ we were working for a long time until now‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_03-ngs002.m4a",
      "text": "お仕事だったから、少しくらいはいいんじゃない？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "so isn’t it okay to relax a bit?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.43333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "そうですね。午前中はリフレッシュして",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’re right. We’ll get refreshed in the morning‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.666666666666664,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_03-ski002.m4a",
      "text": "午後から新曲のヒント探しに専念でも……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "and then focus on looking for ideas for the new song in the afternoon…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "甘い！　渚も沙季も甘いですわ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Naive! Nagisa‚ Saki‚ you’re so naive!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_03-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "そんなことではトップアイドルになれませんわよ！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We won’t get to be top idols if we keep doing this!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 66.66666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "あの麻奈様だって、オフなんてないくらいの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Mana-sama had her schedule so packed‚ she never took",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 70.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_03-suz002.m4a",
      "text": "過密スケジュールをこなしつつ、数々の名曲を――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "any time off‚ and she wrote so many songs…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 73.36666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "はーい、かき氷買ってきたよ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Here it is! I bought shaved ice for everyone!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.9,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-01.m4a",
