        "en": "Suzu-chan‚ you change your stance so quickly!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 96.36666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "さっき言ってたことと矛盾してるじゃないですか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Doesn’t this contradict with what you were saying earlier?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 99.76666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
