      "text": "すずにゃんは可愛いな～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’re so cute‚ Suzu-nyan~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 120.03333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "ちょっ、頭を撫でるのはやめてくれません？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Would you please stop patting me on the head?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 122.96666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_03-suz005.m4a",
      "text": "あなたと私は一つしか違わないでしょう！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You are only one year older than I am!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 126.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
